{
  "stem": "24614.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I'm sure if I would have seen his face, I would have recognized him-- must have been from our neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Nobody walked over to help that child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't-- I'm sure that the child died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] We sat down in the basement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Everybody looked out, I guess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And everybody felt different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Nobody said a word.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My mother [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] said to us, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we're still alive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So let's try and live.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] We waited in the basement for two, three days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "My daddy finally found in the hallway some water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I think that he took a chance and walked in, in the store, because he brought us back not cake, a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I remember it very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was so big, maybe as big as my hand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we waited for Mr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Yeager to come back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When he came back, he said, I found a place for you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But you can't go in the daytime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We will have to go at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he brought us to a place, a family, Catholic family, the Adams, where we were in hiding there for three months or so.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "That family-- first, I want to make sure that the world understands that no matter what we gave that family, they gave us more.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They gave us life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They hid us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they put their life in danger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They were Catholics.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They had six children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I will speak about one of them who just sent me a Christmas card that I have.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And we will show it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
